{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/revival","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Gatsby로 부활한 블로그","date":"January 2nd, 2020"},"html":"<p>타의적으로 못생긴 Hexo를 버리고 자의적으로 못생긴 Gatsby를 채택했어요.</p>\n<p>이 글은 첫 글이에요.</p>\n<p>쓸 말이 없군요. 잘 나오나 테스트나 하려구요.</p>\n<hr>\n<h3>세번째로 큰 헤딩!</h3>\n<p><em>굵은 글씨</em></p>\n<p>역시 마크다운은 타이포라가 짱이에요.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 650px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f874adbe9532a43c129ead25395b7e0b/6c89e/doorkeeperdog.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 133.33333333333331%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"테스트용 수문장 댕댕이\"\n        title=\"수문장 댕댕이\"\n        src=\"/static/f874adbe9532a43c129ead25395b7e0b/53025/doorkeeperdog.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f874adbe9532a43c129ead25395b7e0b/e7722/doorkeeperdog.jpg 163w,\n/static/f874adbe9532a43c129ead25395b7e0b/bdb37/doorkeeperdog.jpg 325w,\n/static/f874adbe9532a43c129ead25395b7e0b/53025/doorkeeperdog.jpg 650w,\n/static/f874adbe9532a43c129ead25395b7e0b/3164d/doorkeeperdog.jpg 975w,\n/static/f874adbe9532a43c129ead25395b7e0b/8d861/doorkeeperdog.jpg 1300w,\n/static/f874adbe9532a43c129ead25395b7e0b/6c89e/doorkeeperdog.jpg 3024w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<pre><code>hi dengdeng\n</code></pre>\n<p>Gatsby 블로그를 만드는 방법에 대한 친절한 가이드를 작성해주신 순호쟝에게 감사를...!</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github